properties.areaDesc: Santa Ana Mountains and Foothills; Orange County Inland; San Bernardino County Mountains
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 3 at 12:59PM PST until February 5 at 9:00AM PST by NWS San Diego CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...For inland Orange County, northeast winds 20 to 30 mph,
with gusts 40 to 50 mph. For the mountains and foothills, north
to northeast winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts up to 60 mph.

* WHERE...San Bernardino County Mountains, Santa Ana Mountains and
Foothills and Orange County Inland Areas. Strongest on south and
southwest facing slopes.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM PST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages
may result. Difficult travel at times for high profile vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PST WEDNESDAY
